🌙 Moonberry Strain – Feminized Cannabis Seeds by Tastebudz Syndicate

Tastebudz Moonberry Strain Seeds offer collectors a bold, terpene-rich experience with serious strength and legacy appeal. Originally released as Blackberry Moonrocks, this 80% Indica strain combines Blue Moonrock and Blackberry Kush to create a fruity-floral profile that’s both nostalgic and elevated.

Now rebranded as Moonberry, this strain maintains all the richness of its original form while gaining recognition for its dense buds, calming effects, and 33% THC potency. Whether you’re after rare genetics, standout flavour, or collector-grade quality, Moonberry brings it all together in one unforgettable strain.

📊 Moonberry Strain Specs

Feature Details
Genetics Blue Moonrock x Blackberry Kush
Strain Type 80% Indica / 20% Sativa
Seed Type Photoperiod Feminized Seeds
THC Content Up to 33%
Flowering Time 8–9 Weeks
Indoor Yield Up to 550g/m²
Outdoor Yield Up to 750g/plant
Flavours Blueberry, blackberry, lavender
Aromas Fruity, floral, earthy
Effects Euphoric, relaxing, long-lasting

🍇 Flavour & Aroma of the Moonberry Strain

Expect a smooth, layered smoke that blends juicy blueberries and blackberries with lavender floral notes. The aroma is deep and fragrant, with hints of earth and spice that round out its fruity character. Each session with the Moonberry strain offers a sensory journey that’s ideal for those who appreciate complex terpenes and lasting flavour.

🌸 Terpene Profile

Moonberry features dominant terpenes like Nerolidol and Linalool, giving it both a floral sweetness and a mildly spicy, herbal finish. These compounds are associated with soothing effects and add depth to the strain’s already rich aroma.

💥 Effects of Moonberry Strain

With up to 33% THC, this strain is not for the faint-hearted. It delivers a powerful body stone that relaxes muscles, eases stress, and leaves you in a euphoric, dream-like state. Great for end-of-day wind-downs or when you need to switch off and reset.

🌟 Why Choose the Moonberry Strain?

  • 🍇 Unmatched Flavour – Juicy dark berries, floral lavender, and earthy undertones
  • 🧬 Renowned Genetics – A premium cross of Blue Moonrock and Blackberry Kush
  • 💪 Ultra-High Potency – 33% THC makes it one of our strongest feminized strains
  • 🌿 Reliable Yields – 550g/m² indoors, up to 750g/plant outdoors
  • 🎨 Visual Appeal – Dense, trichome-coated buds with purple hues
  • 🧠 Collector-Approved – Formerly Blackberry Moonrocks, now rebranded for the modern collector
  • 🔁 Also Available as an Auto – Moonberry Pie Autoflowering Seeds offer faster results with the same terp-rich profile
  • 🎁 Part of Our Mix Pack – Included in the Feminized Cannabis Seed Mix Pack

❓ Frequently Asked Questions About Moonberry Strain

1. What is the Moonberry strain?
Moonberry is a photoperiod feminized cannabis strain bred from Blue Moonrock and Blackberry Kush, known for its deep berry flavour and high THC content.

2. Was Moonberry previously called Blackberry Moonrocks?
Yes — it was originally sold as Blackberry Moonrocks but rebranded as Moonberry to reflect its modern appeal and berry-forward terpene profile.

3. How potent is Moonberry?
Very. It contains up to 33% THC, making it one of the strongest strains in the Tastebudz feminized lineup.

4. Is there an autoflowering version of Moonberry?
Yes! Moonberry Pie Auto offers a faster cycle with the same flavour-rich genetics.

5. Is Moonberry included in any multipacks?
Absolutely — it’s featured in our Feminized Mix Pack, alongside other fan favourites.
